11 An Act relating to the Department of Human Services;
making an appropriation; stating purpose; requiring
12 that certain funds be utilized for certain purpose;
requiring certain funding be maintained at certain
13 levels; requiring certain joint approval prior to
certain actions; requiring certain transfers to
14 certain funds; appropriating certain federal funds
for certain program; authorizing early allocation of
15 funds under certain conditions; authorizing certain
transfers; requiring the maintenance of certain
16 records; providing budgeting and expenditure
limitations and procedures; requiring and prohibiting
17 certain budget procedures; providing an effective
date; and declaring an emergency.
